extendedInfo.description: Name FinderName meanings -- where does your name come from?Truly FREE app, no ads!One of the things that all people have in common is name. Have you ever asked yourself, "What does my name mean?". Most people have some idea of their name meaning or where their name came from. This app has been set up as a free etymology resource to look up the history and meaning of names. Uncover thousands of names and discover the meaning of names, their origins, pronunciations and more.
